    Examples:
      | import set                                            | symbol | output |
      | (only (prefix (foo) my-) my-foo)                      | my-foo | A      |
      | (rename (prefix (foo) my-) (my-foo my-baz))           | my-baz | A      |
      | (except (prefix (rename (foo) (bar baz)) my-) my-foo) | my-baz | B      |

